      • getStoreFileScanner

        public StoreFileScanner getStoreFileScanner(boolean cacheBlocks,
                                            boolean pread,
                                            boolean isCompaction,
                                            long readPt,
                                            long scannerOrder,
                                            boolean canOptimizeForNonNullColumn)
        Get a scanner to scan over this StoreFile.
        Parameters:
        cacheBlocks - should this scanner cache blocks?
        pread - use pread (for highly concurrent small readers)
        isCompaction - is scanner being used for compaction?
        scannerOrder - Order of this scanner relative to other scanners. See KeyValueScanner.getScannerOrder().
        canOptimizeForNonNullColumn - true if we can make sure there is no null column, otherwise false. This is a hint for optimization.
        Returns:
        a scanner

        pread - use pread (for concurrent small readers)
